title: Hour 2 - Peyton Manning (04-20-20)

description:
Peyton Manning talks about playing golf with Tiger Wood; but said he never played golf against Michael Jordan. Peyton also gives Dan a wonderlic question and says the wonderlic does not matter when it comes to the success of a quarterback.
